{"tid":1968977,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★食環職員控訴七宗罪：要淘寶購保護衣","createTime":"2020-04-12T06:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T13:47:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e878b2ac065cbe2c002220a7f66867adb6468404","tid":1968977,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"保護衣要「慳住用」 穿同一件到多個單位<br />\n<br />\n之前青衣長康邨曾爆發個案，涉可能經喉管傳播。另一食環署職員Y小姐表示，工作時經常接觸馬桶、喉管，有需要時更會到劏房工作，認為如果同一座向單位有確診者，或增加工作風險。她表示，雖然部門有提供保護衣，但數量不足，上司亦指「慳住用」，故會穿同一件保護衣，走訪多個單位，擔心會傳播病毒。她又指，每區滲水辦的防護裝備都略有不同，部分未能提供手套，或由上司私下購買；亦<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有地區的上司稱，需「淘寶」購買保護衣</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/458518/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A7%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%83%E5%AE%97%E7%BD%AA-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A8%ADdirty-team-%E8%A6%81%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F458518%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A8%25ADdirty-team-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B7%2598%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25A1%25A3&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WwweZXAU%2BhIfMqCJmwSRnXM%3D&h=caedb54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/458518/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A7%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%83%E5%AE%97%E7%BD%AA-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A8%ADdirty-team-%E8%A6%81%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%A3</a>"},{"pid":"335eaa3ab1235c75d31f0f0f06b0af4fed5e14f8","tid":1968977,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:09:50.000Z","msg